Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.74,0:03:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\pos(220,20)}驴子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.10,0:03:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,那是个战壕吗\N{\fs14\}Is that a trench?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.48,0:03:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,里面好像还有好几只\N{\fs14\}It looks like there's more of them inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.35,0:03:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,E26呼叫指挥\N{\fs14\}Echo 2-6 to command.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.04,0:03:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,上校  北面树林发现三只金刚  其中一只有武器\N{\fs14\}Colonel, we've got eyes on 3 kongs in the north woods. One of them is armed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.50,0:03:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,驴子发现了另一条战壕  基地可能就在附近\N{\fs14\}Our donkey just spotted another trench. Maybe the base is near.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.03,0:04:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,是 长官\N{\fs14\}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.76,0:04:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,是 长官 收到 完毕\N{\fs14\}Yes, sir. Copy. Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.60,0:04:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 驴子\N{\fs14\}Donkey.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.73,0:04:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,普里彻\N{\fs14\}Preacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.82,0:04:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,带枪的那个\N{\fs14\}The one with the gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.76,0:04:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- 把他放倒之后 拿下战壕  - 是 长官\N{\fs14\}- As soon he guns him down, you guys take out the trench. - Yes, sir.Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.57,0:04:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,开火\N{\fs14\}Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.08,0:05:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,冲啊\N{\fs14\}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.31,0:06:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,给我箭\N{\fs14\}Reload.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.73,0:07:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,撤退 撤退\N{\fs14\}Fall back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.64,0:07:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,上校 收得到吗 上校\N{\fs14\}Colonel, do you copy? Colonel?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.14,0:07:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你是谁  - 我是普里彻 长官\N{\fs14\}- Who is this?  - Preacher, sir. Preacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.43,0:07:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你在哪里 士兵 告诉我你的位置\N{\fs14\}Where are you, soldier?I need your position.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.84,0:07:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我不知道  - 那你能看到什么\N{\fs14\}- I don't know. - What do you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.28,0:07:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,什么都看不到 长官  我们损失惨重 上尉他牺牲了\N{\fs14\}I can't see anything, sir. We lost a lot of men and captain is dead, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.79,0:08:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- 行了 冷静点 现在由你指挥  - 由我指挥吗\N{\fs14\}- Calm down. You're in command now. - Command, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.88,0:08:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我想现在只剩下我一个人了\N{\fs14\}I think it’s just me by myself now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.33,0:08:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,上校 我想我可能坚持不住了 长官\N{\fs14\}Colonel, I don’t think I'm gonna make it, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.89,0:08:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉 真的很抱歉 长官\N{\fs14\}I am sorry. I am so sorry, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.38,0:08:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 杀死一只是一只\N{\fs14\}Listen to me. Kill as many as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.77,0:08:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不 不\N{\fs14\}No. No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.49,0:09:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,死了63个\N{\fs14\}63 dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.22,0:09:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你是他 你就是凯撒\N{\fs14\}You are him. You're Caesar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.97,0:09:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我们找了你很久了\N{\fs14\}We've been searching for you for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.60,0:09:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,传说你有一个秘密基地 可我们一直都没能找到\N{\fs14\}We heard you had a hidden command base, but we could never find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.14,0:09:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,有人说你可能已经死了\N{\fs14\}Some of us were starting to think that you might be dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.62,0:10:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,可麦卡洛上校说你一定还在某个地方\N{\fs14\}but the Colonel McCullough said you were out here somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.32,0:10:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 杀了我们得了  - 闭嘴\N{\fs14\}- Just kill us already. - Shut up, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.11,0:10:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 他们是畜生 他早晚会宰了我们的\N{\fs14\}What? They're animals. He's gonna slaughter us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.80,0:10:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,战争并不是由我挑起的\N{\fs14\}I did not start this war.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.53,0:10:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,始作俑者已经死了\N{\fs14\}The ape who did is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.13,0:10:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,他叫科巴\N{\fs14\}His name was Koba.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.47,0:10:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,是我杀了他\N{\fs14\}I killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.73,0:10:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- 现在 我只是想要保护我的同类  - 是吗\N{\fs14\}- Now I fight only to protect apes.  - Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.19,0:10:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那么他呢 还有其他10个像他这样的\N{\fs14\}What about him? We got ten more just like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.31,0:10:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道这些家伙 他们跟随科巴\N{\fs14\}I know these apes. They followed Koba.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.46,0:10:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,他们想要杀了我\N{\fs14\}They tried to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.95,0:10:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他们害怕我会报复他们\N{\fs14\}They fear what I will do to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.44,0:10:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,所以\N{\fs14\}So now
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.54,0:11:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,他们选择为你们做事\N{\fs14\}they serve you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.12,0:11:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,为了生存下去\N{\fs14\}just to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.74,0:11:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我并不怕你\N{\fs14\}I no fear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.70,0:11:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你才应该害怕\N{\fs14\}You must fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.46,0:11:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得这片树林还能保护你们多久\N{\fs14\}How long you think woods can protect you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.83,0:11:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,人类会消灭你们\N{\fs14\}Humans destroy you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.91,0:11:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,他们的上校非常强大\N{\fs14\}Their Colonel has all power.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.52,0:11:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,对他们而言 他不是一个普通人\N{\fs14\}For them, he more than just human.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.21,0:11:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,他掌控一切\N{\fs14\}He everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.37,0:11:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他说先杀了凯撒\N{\fs14\}He say: "First Caesar die?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.34,0:11:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来就轮到你们了\N{\fs14\}then all of you die."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.49,0:11:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,温特 把这叛徒带出去\N{\fs14\}Winter! Take this traitor outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.24,0:12:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么处置这些人类\N{\fs14\}What should we do with the humans?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.13,0:12:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你要放我们走\N{\fs14\}You are letting us go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.28,0:12:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉你们上校 你见到我了\N{\fs14\}Tell your Colonel, you have seen me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.40,0:12:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我还有句话要你带给他 只要人类退出树林\N{\fs14\}And I have a message for him. Leave us the woods?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.49,0:12:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,杀戮就能够停止\N{\fs14\}and the killing can stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.88,0:12:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得他们会把话带到吗\N{\fs14\}Do you think they will give him the message?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.82,0:12:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,他们本身就是消息 毛里斯\N{\fs14\}They are the message, Maurice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.04,0:12:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,他会知道我们并不是野蛮人\N{\fs14\}He will see we are not savages.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.09,0:13:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那个叛徒袭击了我 被他逃走了\N{\fs14\}The traitor attacked me! He got away!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.16,0:13:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,科巴始终阴魂不散\N{\fs14\}Koba still haunts us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.12,0:13:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么当时我看不出 他根本无法原谅人类对他做的事\N{\fs14\}What I didn't see that he could not forgive what humans did to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.59,0:13:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,没人知道他的内心\N{\fs14\}No one could have known how much darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.08,0:13:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,有多么黑暗\N{\fs14\}was living inside him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.45,0:14:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,父亲\N{\fs14\}Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.19,0:14:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎回家 火箭\N{\fs14\}Welcome home, Rocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.50,0:14:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你看上去很累\N{\fs14\}You look tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.15,0:14:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这次路途非常遥远  - 父亲 我们有发现\N{\fs14\}- It was a long journey. - Father, we found something!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.91,0:14:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧\N{\fs14\}Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.58,0:15:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,母亲\N{\fs14\}Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.37,0:15:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,科尼利厄斯 和你哥哥打个招呼\N{\fs14\}Cornelius... Say hi to your brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.14,0:15:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子 快看那是谁\N{\fs14\}Look who's here, son...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.02,0:15:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,蕾可\N{\fs14\}Lake...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.85,0:16:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这个地方 父亲 我们可以重新开始 一个新家园\N{\fs14\}This is it, Father. We can start over. A new home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.44,0:16:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那些山后面是什么 孩子  - 让大家看看 火箭\N{\fs14\}- What is beyond those mountains, son? - Show them, Rocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.99,0:16:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,一片沙漠 那里离这儿很远\N{\fs14\}A desert! The journey is long...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.31,0:16:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,也正因为这样人类才不会找到我们\N{\fs14\}But that is why humans will not find us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.18,0:17:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我们今晚就得出发\N{\fs14\}We must leave tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.20,0:17:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚 这怎么可能\N{\fs14\}Tonight? That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.43,0:17:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们还能熬多久 蕾可 士兵已经逼近了  - 温特\N{\fs14\}- How long can we wait, Lake? Soldiers getting closer! - Winter...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.07,0:17:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你的儿子离开太久了 凯撒\N{\fs14\}Your son's been gone, Caesar...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.46,0:17:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,他不知道我们有多艰难\N{\fs14\}He doesn't know how hard it's been.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.14,0:17:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你很害怕\N{\fs14\}I know you are scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.54,0:17:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都一样\N{\fs14\}We all are...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.18,0:17:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,可我们还得计划一下\N{\fs14\}But we are still planning...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.65,0:17:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 我们得找个安全的方法离开树林\N{\fs14\}Yes. We must find a safe way out of woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.99,0:17:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,之前因为只有你们两个\N{\fs14\}There were only two of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.42,0:17:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,可现在目标太大了\N{\fs14\}But we are many.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.43,0:18:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会找到办法离开这里的\N{\fs14\}We will find a way out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.62,0:18:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,团结才会强大\N{\fs14\}Apes together strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.30,0:19:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,待在这儿 孩子 保护好你的母亲和弟弟\N{\fs14\}Stay here, son. Protect your mother and brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.39,0:20:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,凯撒 出什么事了\N{\fs14\}Caesar! What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.39,0:20:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,有多少兄弟在巡逻\N{\fs14\}How many on patrol?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.23,0:20:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- 五六个吧  - 把他们找来\N{\fs14\}- Five? Six? - Get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.05,0:20:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,卢卡 把火箭也找来\N{\fs14\}Luca, get Rocket too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.35,0:21:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,L4呼叫指挥 上校\N{\fs14\}Unit calling command. Colonel...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.63,0:21:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- 火箭 发生什么事了  - 我听到他说的话了 上校就在这里\N{\fs14\}- Rocket? What happened? - I heard him talking! Colonel is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.51,0:21:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,99 目标已击毙\N{\fs14\}Ninety-nine, target acquired.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.54,0:21:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,99 目标已击毙 重复 金刚已经死了\N{\fs14\}Ninety-nine, target acquired. Repeat, King Kong is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.75,0:21:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我们走 赶紧撤离这里\N{\fs14\}Let's go. I get up from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.54,0:23:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,凯撒 温特不见了\N{\fs14\}Caesar... We can't find Winter!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.10,0:23:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,他之前很害怕 我想他背叛了我们\N{\fs14\}He was scared! I think he betrayed us!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.17,0:24:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,找到科尼利厄斯了吗\N{\fs14\}Have you found Cornelius yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.46,0:24:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还在找\N{\fs14\}We're still searching.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.21,0:24:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我们去找凯撒的小儿子\N{\fs14\}Let's go look for Caesar’s little son.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.16,0:24:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,科尼利厄斯\N{\fs14\}Come, Cornelius.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.66,0:25:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你安全了\N{\fs14\}You're safe now.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.55,0:25:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,蕾可\N{\fs14\}Lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.80,0:25:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,, 你爱我的儿子\N{\fs14\}You loved my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.15,0:25:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,在我回来之前 照顾好他的弟弟\N{\fs14\}Look after his brother, until I return.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.77,0:25:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你不和我们一起去新家园吗\N{\fs14\}You're not coming with us to our new home?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.91,0:25:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs14\}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.56,0:25:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,跟着蕾可\N{\fs14\}Go with Lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.01,0:26:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,凯撒 你该不会想要去找他们吧\N{\fs14\}Caesar! You're not going after them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.92,0:26:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不是他们 是他\N{\fs14\}Not them, him.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.64,0:26:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,凯撒 你是我们的首领\N{\fs14\}Caesar, you are our leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.81,0:26:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不能没有你\N{\fs14\}We can't leave without you!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.69,0:26:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须去\N{\fs14\}You must.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.25,0:26:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,那些士兵很快会回来的\N{\fs14\}The soldiers will be back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.39,0:26:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸\N{\fs14\}Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.95,0:26:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦找到他 所有的士兵都会来追我\N{\fs14\}When I find him, the soldiers will all come after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.06,0:26:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,到时就是你们离开的最佳时机\N{\fs14\}That makes you the best chance to get out of woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.44,0:26:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,他要去哪里\N{\fs14\}Where is he going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.30,0:26:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,凯撒 凯撒\N{\fs14\}Caesar! Caesar!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.82,0:27:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那些士兵的营地一直在转移\N{\fs14\}The soldiers' camp is always moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.36,0:27:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我的手下知道他们在哪儿\N{\fs14\}My guards think they know where it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.00,0:27:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我带你去 - 你需要我的支援\N{\fs14\}- Let me take you. - You need me to back you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.21,0:27:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs14\}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.74,0:27:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了 我知道失去儿子是什么感觉\N{\fs14\}Please... I know what it's like to lose a son.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.71,0:28:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我可能没法活着回去\N{\fs14\}I may not make it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.34,0:28:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我才要跟着你\N{\fs14\}That's why I'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.35,0:28:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,确保你能安全回来\N{\fs14\}To make sure you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.78,0:28:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我的手下认为士兵就在这儿 总是有火在烧\N{\fs14\}Guards think soldiers here... Always fires burning.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.11,0:29:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这里没人\N{\fs14\}No one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.55,0:29:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,四处搜一下\N{\fs14\}Search the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.81,0:29:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是放下手上的东西\N{\fs14\}Just gonna put this down.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.05,0:30:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,他一个人在这儿干吗\N{\fs14\}What's he doing out here alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.71,0:30:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,或许他是个逃兵\N{\fs14\}Maybe he's a deserter?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.34,0:31:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,到处看看\N{\fs14\}Look around.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.23,0:31:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,能用的都带走\N{\fs14\}Take what you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.77,0:33:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,她有点不对劲 我想她不会说话\N{\fs14\}Something wrong with her. I don't think she can speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.75,0:33:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧\N{\fs14\}Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.41,0:33:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,她一个人在这儿会死的\N{\fs14\}She'll die out here alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.78,0:34:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不能带上她 毛里斯\N{\fs14\}We cannot take her, Maurice.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.15,0:34:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我理解 可我不能丢下她\N{\fs14\}I understand... But I cannot leave her.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.15,0:35:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\pos(192,25)}只有死了的金刚才是好金刚
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.30,0:35:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,找到上校了吗\N{\fs14\}Did you find the Colonel?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.51,0:35:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\fs14\}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.38,0:35:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,温特\N{\fs14\}Winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.21,0:35:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\pos(192,25)}驴子
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.73,0:35:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,上校在哪里\N{\fs14\}Where is the Colonel?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.94,0:35:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他走了  - 走了\N{\fs14\}- He's gone. - Gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.09,0:36:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,今天早上走的 带了许多人一起\N{\fs14\}He left this morning, took many men with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.58,0:36:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,还会有更多士兵从北方过来\N{\fs14\}More soldiers are coming down from the North.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.15,0:36:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,上校打算去边界和他们会合\N{\fs14\}The Colonel is going to meet them at the border.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.52,0:36:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,什么边界 为什么\N{\fs14\}What border? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.36,0:36:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fs14\}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.72,0:36:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不过我们明天会跟着去\N{\fs14\}But the rest of us are going tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.37,0:36:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,驴子们觉得北方的这些士兵\N{\fs14\}Donkeys think the soldiers from the North
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.41,0:36:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是来彻底消灭猿类的\N{\fs14\}are coming to help finish off the apes for good.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.62,0:36:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那天 就在山上那一战之后\N{\fs14\}That day, after the battle on the hill,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.62,0:36:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我们抓住的那只驴子向我保证 上校会饶我一命\N{\fs14\}the donkey we caught promised me the Colonel would spare my life
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.18,0:36:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,只要我告诉他们你藏在哪里\N{\fs14\}if I told them where you were hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.17,0:36:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,原谅我\N{\fs14\}Forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.12,0:36:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我的儿子\N{\fs14\}My son...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.48,0:36:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我的妻子\N{\fs14\}My wife...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.76,0:37:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,全都死了\N{\fs14\}are dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.42,0:38:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,现在该怎么办\N{\fs14\}Now what do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.93,0:38:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,等士兵们出发\N{\fs14\}Wait till the soldiers go...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.45,0:38:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,跟着他们去找上校\N{\fs14\}Follow them to the Colonel.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.39,0:38:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,科巴\N{\fs14\}Koba?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.56,0:39:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,猿类不杀猿类\N{\fs14\}Ape not kill ape.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.88,0:39:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,士兵们要离开了\N{\fs14\}The soldiers are leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.88,0:39:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,他们停下了\N{\fs14\}They stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.14,0:40:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在朝谁开枪\N{\fs14\}What are they shooting at?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.02,0:40:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道\N{\fs14\}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.38,0:41:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,他们为什么朝你们开枪\N{\fs14\}Why did they shoot you?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.18,0:42:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,和她一样\N{\fs14\}Like her!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.27,0:42:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,他说不出话来\N{\fs14\}He cannot speak!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.70,0:42:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,伤势那么重 他会死的\N{\fs14\}He will die of those wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.31,0:42:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,卢卡\N{\fs14\}Luca.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.53,0:42:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那些士兵去哪儿了\N{\fs14\}Where did the soldiers go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.80,0:42:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,温特说他们会去某个边界\N{\fs14\}Winter said they were going to a border.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.47,0:42:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 可往哪条路走呢\N{\fs14\}Yes but which way is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.22,0:46:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,坏 猴子\N{\fs14\}Bad... ape.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.82,0:46:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,坏 猴子\N{\fs14\}Bad ape.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.24,0:46:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你是谁\N{\fs14\}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.14,0:47:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你在这里做什么\N{\fs14\}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.16,0:47:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我想他不懂我们的意思\N{\fs14\}I don't think he understands.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.92,0:47:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我不认识他 他不是我们的一员\N{\fs14\}I don't recognize him. He's not one of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.85,0:47:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,只有你一个吗\N{\fs14\}Are you alone here?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.60,0:47:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,冷\N{\fs14\}Cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.48,0:47:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,冷\N{\fs14\}Cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.63,0:48:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我看见女孩儿 以为你们是人类\N{\fs14\}I see girl. I think you human.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.06,0:48:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,原来你们是猿类 和我一样\N{\fs14\}But you ape. Like me!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.47,0:48:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不 不要动\N{\fs14\}No, no. Put down.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.12,0:48:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你待在这里多久了  - 很久了 很久很久\N{\fs14\}- How long have you been here? - Long time. Long... long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.18,0:48:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,家\N{\fs14\}Home.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.84,0:48:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我以前的家\N{\fs14\}Old home.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.43,0:48:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\pos(192,25)}西拉动物园
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.66,0:48:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你还有同伴吗\N{\fs14\}Are there more like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.97,0:48:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- 动物园里其他的猿类  - 死了 全都死了\N{\fs14\}- More apes... from zoo? - Dead. All dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.57,0:48:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,很久以前 人类生病了\N{\fs14\}Long time. Human get sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.13,0:48:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,猿类变聪明了\N{\fs14\}Ape get smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.69,0:48:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,然后人类杀死猿类 可我没被杀\N{\fs14\}Then human kill ape. But not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.36,0:48:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我跑了\N{\fs14\}I run.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.59,0:49:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你学会了说话  - 听人类说\N{\fs14\}- You learned to speak? - Listened human.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.95,0:49:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,坏猴子\N{\fs14\}"Bad ape!"
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.61,0:49:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,坏猴子\N{\fs14\}Bad ape.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.16,0:49:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs14\}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.93,0:49:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不要碰\N{\fs14\}No touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.98,0:49:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那个是我的\N{\fs14\}That's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.20,0:49:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我没事\N{\fs14\}I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.06,0:49:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,真了不起\N{\fs14\}Amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.87,0:49:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我还以为只有我们会说话\N{\fs14\}Always thought we were the only ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.55,0:49:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道世上还有没有其他\N{\fs14\}Wonder if there are more in the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.60,0:49:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,像我们一样的猿类\N{\fs14\}More apes like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.28,0:49:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,来 吃啊 吃\N{\fs14\}Here. Eat. Eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.79,0:49:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,新朋友\N{\fs14\}New friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.01,0:50:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,特殊的日子\N{\fs14\}Special day.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.66,0:50:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\pos(192,25)}加利福尼亚边界检疫站 塔岩
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.96,0:50:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\pos(192,25)}边界
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.62,0:50:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这是从哪儿弄来的\N{\fs14\}Where did you get this?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.22,0:50:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,坏地方\N{\fs14\}Bad place.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.49,0:50:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我很久以前找到的 离开动物园后我寻找食物\N{\fs14\}I find long time ago. After zoo I look for food.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.78,0:50:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我发现了人类动物园\N{\fs14\}I find human zoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.05,0:50:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,全都是生病的人\N{\fs14\}Zoo for sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.72,0:50:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,很高的墙 生病的人 爬墙\N{\fs14\}Big walls. Sick human climb.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.31,0:50:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,坏人类 杀他们\N{\fs14\}Bad human kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.35,0:50:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,然后 所有人都生病\N{\fs14\}And then all get sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.26,0:50:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,所有人都死了 很久以前 很久很久\N{\fs14\}All dead now. Long time. Long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.85,0:50:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,坏人类\N{\fs14\}Bad humans?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.86,0:50:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,士兵吗\N{\fs14\}Soldiers?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.33,0:50:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- 士兵  - 一个废弃的军营\N{\fs14\}- Soldiers. - A deserted military camp!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.56,0:50:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,就在边界\N{\fs14\}On the border!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.86,0:50:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,或许上校和军队就是去那儿了\N{\fs14\}Maybe the Colonel and the troops are going there?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.09,0:50:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那儿离这儿远吗 你能带我们去吗\N{\fs14\}Is it far? Can you take us?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.19,0:51:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,人类动物园\N{\fs14\}Human zoo?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.44,0:51:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不 不回那儿去\N{\fs14\}No! No go back there. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.92,0:51:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,所有人都死了 我才来这儿 这儿非常安全\N{\fs14\}Everyone dead. I come here. Very safe here.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.48,0:51:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不要回去\N{\fs14\}Never go back! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.04,0:51:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- 求你了 你必须带我们去那儿  - 不\N{\fs14\}- Please. You must take us. - No!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.79,0:51:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不能去 不能去 不 不\N{\fs14\}No! Cannot take! Cannot take! No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.20,0:51:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不 看啊 看啊\N{\fs14\}No! Look! Look! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.88,0:51:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,很多雪 不能走 留在这儿\N{\fs14\}More snow. Cannot go. Must stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.64,0:51:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你能吃 你能休息 和我一起 留在这儿\N{\fs14\}You eat, you rest, stay here. With me.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.08,0:51:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,给 给你\N{\fs14\}Here. You keep.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.33,0:51:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,给她了\N{\fs14\}She keep.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.03,0:51:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\pos(192,25)}诺娃
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.43,0:52:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,是谁\N{\fs14\}Who is...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.72,0:52:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那孩子\N{\fs14\}child?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.31,0:52:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fs14\}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.21,0:52:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,可她跟着你\N{\fs14\}But she with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.14,0:52:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,她没有别的同伴了\N{\fs14\}She has no one else.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.62,0:52:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚才看你看着她\N{\fs14\}I see you look at her just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.25,0:52:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,眼神很悲伤\N{\fs14\}Look sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.43,0:52:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你也有孩子吗\N{\fs14\}You have child?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.78,0:52:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,一个\N{\fs14\}One.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.57,0:52:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,另一个被人类杀死了\N{\fs14\}The other was killed by human.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.75,0:52:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,士兵吗\N{\fs14\}Soldier?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.14,0:53:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我\N{\fs14\}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.94,0:53:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,也有孩子\N{\fs14\}Had child.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.23,0:53:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得人类动物园里\N{\fs14\}You think you will find him...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.24,0:53:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,能找到他吗\N{\fs14\}at human zoo?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.22,0:53:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,那个士兵\N{\fs14\}Soldier?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.20,0:53:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fs14\}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.22,0:53:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,或许吧\N{\fs14\}Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.15,0:53:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那么\N{\fs14\}Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.50,0:54:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那我带你去吧\N{\fs14\}Maybe I take you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.76,0:55:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,口渴\N{\fs14\}Thirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.68,0:55:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,口渴\N{\fs14\}Thirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.32,0:55:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,口渴\N{\fs14\}Thirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.24,0:56:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,走 卢卡 我们靠近点\N{\fs14\}Luca, come. Let's go closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.09,0:56:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,保护好他们\N{\fs14\}Keep them safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.86,0:56:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在干吗\N{\fs14\}What are they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.88,0:56:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道\N{\fs14\}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.13,0:56:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么 巡逻队吗\N{\fs14\}What's that? A patrol?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.82,0:56:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,马上没有人\N{\fs14\}I don't see riders.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.72,0:56:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,别动\N{\fs14\}Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.51,0:56:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到他们过来了\N{\fs14\}I saw them coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.42,0:57:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,至少这次\N{\fs14\}At least this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.54,0:57:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我保护了你\N{\fs14\}I was able to protect you...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.35,0:58:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,凯撒\N{\fs14\}Caesar...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.46,0:58:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,该停下了\N{\fs14\}This must stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.91,0:58:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,现在回去找大家还不迟\N{\fs14\}It's not too late to join the other apes.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.80,0:58:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不能回头\N{\fs14\}We cannot turn back!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.29,0:58:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,卢卡献出了自己的生命\N\N{\fs14\}Luca gave his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.15,0:58:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了\N{\fs14\}Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.37,0:58:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,他们必须付出代价\N{\fs14\}They must pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.76,0:59:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,现在的你\N{\fs14\}Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.87,0:59:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,听起来就像科巴\N{\fs14\}you sound like Koba.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.41,0:59:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,带你们一起来就是个错误\N{\fs14\}It was a mistake bringing you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.95,0:59:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我的战争\N{\fs14\}This is my fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.38,0:59:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须一个人去了结了它\N{\fs14\}I will finish this alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.92,0:59:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,回去 快\N{\fs14\}Go. Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.85,0:59:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,去找大部队\N{\fs14\}Join the others.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.60,1:00:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,发生了什么事\N{\fs14\}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.79,1:01:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,他们突然出现\N{\fs14\}They came out of nowhere...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.75,1:01:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,攻击了我们\N{\fs14\}Attacked us.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.77,1:01:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我们以为他们会把我们通通杀死\N{\fs14\}We thought they would kill us all...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.56,1:01:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,但上校阻止了他们\N{\fs14\}But the Colonel stopped them!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.76,1:01:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他眼神里流露着疯狂\N{\fs14\}There was madness in his eyes!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.57,1:01:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,他说要在我们死之前好好利用我们\N{\fs14\}He said they would use us, before we died!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:19.39,1:01:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,于是他们就把我们全都带到了这里\N{\fs14\}And they brought us all here!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.67,1:01:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,利用你们\N{\fs14\}Use you?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.82,1:01:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,他们逼迫我们干活\N{\fs14\}They've been forcing us to work!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.53,1:01:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fs14\}What...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.55,1:01:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,让你们干什么样的活儿\N{\fs14\}What kind of work?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.12,1:01:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 我的儿子 他在这儿吗\N{\fs14\}Wait. My little son is here.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.91,1:01:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,格兰特\N{\fs14\}Grant...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.09,1:01:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,和李\N{\fs14\}and Lee.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.12,1:02:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,惠林顿\N{\fs14\}Wellington...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.75,1:02:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,和拿破仑\N{\fs14\}and Napoleon.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.10,1:02:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,卡斯特\N{\fs14\}Custer
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.66,1:02:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,还有酋长坐牛\N{\fs14\}and Sitting Bull...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.23,1:02:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你可能没怎么看过书吧\N{\fs14\}You’re probably not much of a reader,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.16,1:02:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不过眼下可是一个非常重要的时刻\N{\fs14\}but this is a big moment.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.53,1:02:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你躲哪儿去了\N{\fs14\}Where were you?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.09,1:02:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我们很走运 遇上了你的猴群\N{\fs14\}We came upon your herd. We got lucky.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.65,1:02:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不过我很惊讶 你居然没和他们一起\N{\fs14\}I was surprised you weren’t with them.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.68,1:02:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望你没有后悔之前放他一条生路\N{\fs14\}I hope you don’t come to regret sparing his life.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.60,1:02:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,他射得很准\N{\fs14\}He's quite a good shot.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.66,1:03:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你最终还是来救你的族群了吗\N{\fs14\}Have you finally come to save your apes?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.66,1:03:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我是冲你来的\N{\fs14\}I came for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.26,1:03:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,冲我？\N{\fs14\}For me?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.40,1:03:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,那晚我杀死的是谁\N{\fs14\}Who did I kill that night?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.39,1:03:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我的妻子\N{\fs14\}My wife.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.96,1:03:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,还有我的儿子\N{\fs14\}My son.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.97,1:03:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\fs14\}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.02,1:03:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我的目标是你\N{\fs14\}I was there for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.18,1:03:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天啊\N{\fs14\}God.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.68,1:03:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,看看你的眼睛\N{\fs14\}Look at your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.62,1:03:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,简直和人类一样\N{\fs14\}Almost human.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.47,1:04:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你怎么知道我在这儿的  - 我收到消息 你会来这儿\N{\fs14\}- How did you know I was here?  - I was told you were coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.48,1:04:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,北方还会有更多士兵\N{\fs14\}That more soldiers from the north...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.57,1:04:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- 会来这里和你会合  - 和我汇合\N{\fs14\}- would be joining you here.  - Joining me?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.18,1:04:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,为了把我们猿类\N{\fs14\}To finish us off.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.62,1:04:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,一举歼灭\N{\fs14\}For good.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.82,1:04:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,谁这么告诉你的\N{\fs14\}Who told you that?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.50,1:04:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs14\}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.18,1:04:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我们走\N{\fs14\}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.18,1:05:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸\N{\fs14\}Father!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:13.08,1:05:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸\N{\fs14\}Father!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.75,1:06:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,蕾可\N{\fs14\}Lake.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.51,1:06:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,原谅他们 我们经历了太多\N{\fs14\}Forgive them. We've been through much.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.37,1:06:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸\N{\fs14\}Father!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.22,1:06:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我到底做了些什么\N{\fs14\}What have I done?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.61,1:07:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,全体都有 立定\N{\fs14\}Battalion, halt!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.91,1:07:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- 鲜血  - 可以滋养青草\N{\fs14\}- Blood!  - Makes the grass grow!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.01,1:07:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们  - 可以献出鲜血\N{\fs14\}- We!  - Make the blood flow!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.49,1:07:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们既是开始  - 也是终结\N{\fs14\}- We are the beginning!  - And the end!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.43,1:08:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\pos(192,25)}♫ 美国国歌《星条旗》♫
Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.03,1:09:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\pos(192,25)}危险 易燃
Dialogue: 0,1:09:34.54,1:09:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,到这儿以后我们就没吃过东西没喝过水\N{\fs14\}We haven't had food or water since we got here...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.56,1:09:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,他们为什么要建这堵墙\N{\fs14\}Why do they need a wall?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.31,1:10:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,驴子\N{\fs14\}Donkey!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.59,1:10:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- 教训他  – 好的\N{\fs14\}- Get him! - Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.34,1:10:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs14\}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.54,1:10:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,别再打了\N{\fs14\}Leave him!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:37.04,1:13:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- 告诉他们全都回去干活  – 我们需要食物和水\N{\fs14\}- Tell them to get back to work. - Apes need food and water.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.66,1:13:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- 告诉他们  – 给他们食物和水\N{\fs14\}- Tell them. - Give them food and water.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.08,1:14:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,五\N{\fs14\}Five.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:01.20,1:14:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,四\N{\fs14\}Four.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.75,1:14:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,三\N{\fs14\}Three.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.86,1:14:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,二\N{\fs14\}Two.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.42,1:14:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,快回去干活\N{\fs14\}Hurry! Back to work!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:46.28,1:14:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,把他绑起来 驴子\N{\fs14\}String him up, donkey.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.19,1:15:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,坏地方\N{\fs14\}Bad place.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:02.49,1:15:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,很坏 很坏的地方\N{\fs14\}Bad, bad place.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.35,1:15:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,看到了什么\N{\fs14\}What you see?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:15.23,1:15:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- 必须救他们  – 怎么救\N{\fs14\}- Must save them! - But how?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.26,1:15:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,想想 凯撒他会怎么做\N{\fs14\}Must think! What would Caesar do?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:22.91,1:15:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs14\}No!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:27.04,1:15:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么这么小\N{\fs14\}Why so small?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:01.48,1:16:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,上校答应了你什么\N{\fs14\}What did the Colonel promised you?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:04.22,1:16:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你真觉得等我们全都死了\N{\fs14\}You really think he let you live?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.38,1:16:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,他会放过你吗\N{\fs14\}After we are gone?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.26,1:16:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你让他们叫你驴子\N{\fs14\}You let them call you donkey.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.43,1:16:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,可你是猿类\N{\fs14\}You are ape.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:25.89,1:16:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,上校要见你\N{\fs14\}Colonel wants see you.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.43,1:16:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\pos(192,25)}历史
Dialogue: 0,1:16:53.29,1:16:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,再敢妨碍他们干活\N{\fs14\}Interfere with the work again,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.10,1:16:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我就把他们一个个全都杀掉\N{\fs14\}I will begin slaughtering the apes, one by one.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:57.82,1:17:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,听懂了吗 我需要那堵墙\N{\fs14\}Understand? I need that wall.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:00.06,1:17:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,猿类需要食物还有水\N{\fs14\}Apes need food and water.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.35,1:17:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,当任务完成后 我自然会给他们食物和水\N{\fs14\}They'll get food and water when they finish their work.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.08,1:17:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,给他们食物和水\N{\fs14\}Give apes food and water.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.01,1:17:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- 否则任务没法完成  – 你太过感情用事了\N{\fs14\}- Or they cannot finish it. - You know, you're very emotional.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:18.45,1:17:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你凭什么觉得你有资本和我讨价还价\N{\fs14\}What makes you think you’re in a position to make demands?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.70,1:17:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好了 我们走  – 北方来的那些士兵\N{\fs14\}- Okay, let's go. - The soldiers who are coming here,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:31.06,1:17:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,并不是来和你们会合的 对吧\N{\fs14\}they are not coming to join you, are they?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:35.72,1:17:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到外墙上的那些士兵正在准备作战\N{\fs14\}I saw men outside, on the wall, preparing for battle.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:43.17,1:17:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,他们都说你很聪明 不过想不到那么聪明\N{\fs14\}They told me you're smart, but that's impressive.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.98,1:17:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,对 他们并不是来会合的\N{\fs14\}No, they won't be joining me.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:51.73,1:17:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他们是你的敌人吗\N{\fs14\}They are against you?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.44,1:17:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,他们怕我\N{\fs14\}They fear me.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.59,1:18:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么 因为你连自己人也杀吗\N{\fs14\}Why? Because you kill your own men?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.19,1:18:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我们发现了尸体\N{\fs14\}We found bodies.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:03.50,1:18:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那几个人很不对劲\N{\fs14\}Something wrong with these men.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:10.14,1:18:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊 你还真是让我大开眼界\N{\fs14\}Jesus Christ, you are impressive.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.03,1:18:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,现在你全都知道了 你肯定觉得我不是好人\N{\fs14\}You paint quite a picture. What you must think of me.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:19.56,1:18:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得你没有怜悯之心\N{\fs14\}I think you have no mercy.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:40.73,1:18:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你来是为了杀我\N{\fs14\}You came here to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:44.07,1:18:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你会对我有怜悯之心吗\N{\fs14\}Were you going to show me mercy?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:46.06,1:18:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我放过了你的人 这就是我对你的怜悯\N{\fs14\}I showed you mercy when I spared your men.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.82,1:18:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我提出了和平相处 可你却杀了我的家人\N{\fs14\}I offered you peace and you killed my family.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.23,1:19:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,怜悯\N{\fs14\}Mercy.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:12.58,1:19:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道你所谓的怜悯给我们带来了什么\N{\fs14\}Do you have any idea what your mercy would do to us?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.89,1:19:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你们比我们强壮\N{\fs14\}You’re much stronger than we are.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.07,1:19:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你们聪明绝顶\N{\fs14\}You're smart as hell.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.32,1:19:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不管你们怎么说 你们终将替代我们\N{\fs14\}No matter what you say, you’d eventually replace us.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.90,1:19:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这是大自然的法则\N{\fs14\}That’s the law of Nature.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.84,1:19:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,讽刺的是 是我们造就了你们\N{\fs14\}The irony is, we created you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.98,1:19:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不断挑战自然 试图征服它\N{\fs14\}We tried to defy Nature, bend it to our will.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.11,1:19:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,于是大自然开始惩罚我们的自以为是\N{\fs14\}And Nature’s been punishing us for our arrogance ever since.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:43.65,1:19:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,十个月前 我派了侦查小组去找你们的营地\N{\fs14\}Ten months ago, I sent out recon units to look for your base.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:47.13,1:19:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我的儿子是其中一个小组的成员\N{\fs14\}My own son was a soldier with one of the units.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:50.77,1:19:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,有一天他突然就不说话\N{\fs14\}One day he suddenly stopped speaking.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:53.06,1:19:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,退化成非常原始的状态 就像动物一样\N{\fs14\}He became primitive, like an animal.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:55.70,1:19:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,他们跑来告诉我\N{\fs14\}They contacted me,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.07,1:20:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,说我的儿子疯了\N{\fs14\}said that they thought he’d lost his mind,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.31,1:20:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,说他承受不住战争的压力\N{\fs14\}that the war was too much for him.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:03.50,1:20:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,然后照顾他的那些人也不会说话了\N{\fs14\}Then the man who cared for him stopped speaking too.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.87,1:20:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,当时的医生提出了一个理论 在他还会说话时\N{\fs14\}Their medic had a theory, before he stopped speaking,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:12.55,1:20:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,即使是幸存者身上也同样携带着\N{\fs14\}that the virus that almost wiped us out,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:15.21,1:20:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这种让人类几乎濒临灭绝的可怕病毒\N{\fs14\}the virus that every human survivor still carries,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.59,1:20:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,现在病毒突变了\N{\fs14\}had suddenly changed.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:21.90,1:20:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,变异了\N{\fs14\}Mutated.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.98,1:20:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,如果传播开来的话 这次人类将会彻底灭亡\N{\fs14\}And if it spread, it would destroy humanity for good this time.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:31.70,1:20:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,它不会杀死我们 但会夺走那些使我们成为人类的东西\N{\fs14\}Not by killing us, but by robbing us of the things that make us human.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:37.35,1:20:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的语言 我们的思想\N{\fs14\}Our speech, our higher thinking.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.13,1:20:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,它会把我们变成野兽 你还在这儿和我谈怜悯\N{\fs14\}It would turn us into beasts. You talk about mercy?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.81,1:20:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,换作你会怎么做\N{\fs14\}What would you have done?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:51.63,1:20:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,当时有那么一刻我非常清醒\N{\fs14\}It was a moment of clarity for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:54.52,1:20:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我意识到我必须牺牲自己唯一的儿子\N{\fs14\}I realized that I would have to sacrifice my only son,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.75,1:21:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这样人类才能得以保全\N{\fs14\}so that humanity could be saved.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:04.74,1:21:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,当时我握着那把枪很久很久\N{\fs14\}I held that gun in my hand for a long time...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.90,1:21:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我拿它指着我唯一的儿子\N{\fs14\}And I pointed it at my only child.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:20.48,1:21:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,他看着我 眼睛里充满了信任\N{\fs14\}He looked at me with trust in his eyes.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:28.21,1:21:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,即便从他原始的眼神中\N{\fs14\}Even in his primitive gaze,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.56,1:21:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我也感受到了\N{\fs14\}I felt his...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.34,1:21:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,他的爱\N{\fs14\}love.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:46.72,1:21:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我扣下了扳机\N{\fs14\}I pulled the trigger.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:50.85,1:21:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我感觉被净化了 也让我的目标变得更加明确\N{\fs14\}It purified me. It made my purpose clear.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.35,1:22:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我下令杀死了其他受到感染的人 所有人\N{\fs14\}I gave orders to kill the others infected, all of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:02.54,1:22:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,把他们的东西 任何可能会传播病毒的东西全都烧掉\N{\fs14\}Burn their belongings, anything that might spread contamination.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:07.42,1:22:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,有些人质疑我的判断力\N{\fs14\}Some of the men questioned my judgment.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:09.95,1:22:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我让他们做出和我一样的选择\N{\fs14\}I was asking them to do what I had done,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:13.07,1:22:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,牺牲他们的朋友们 他们的家人\N{\fs14\}to sacrifice their friends, their family.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:20.71,1:22:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,当然 他们拒绝了\N{\fs14\}Of course, they refused.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:25.97,1:22:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我把他们也杀了\N{\fs14\}I had them killed too.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:29.85,1:22:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,有些带着孩子的 偷偷逃进了树林里\N{\fs14\}Others with children deserted into the woods.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.56,1:22:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,其中有个家伙逃到了我在北方的上级那里\N{\fs14\}One of those cowards fled to my superiors up north.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:39.57,1:22:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他们试图说服我\N{\fs14\}They tried to convince me
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.47,1:22:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这场瘟疫可以通过医疗手段得以控制\N{\fs14\}that this plague could be dealt with medically.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:44.91,1:22:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那时我知道 经历了那么多之后 他们还是什么都没学到\N{\fs14\}That’s when I realized that they had learned nothing from our past.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:52.86,1:22:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你把他们也杀了\N{\fs14\}You killed them too?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:57.10,1:22:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我是怎么做的来着 普里彻\N{\fs14\}What did I do, Preacher?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:00.25,1:23:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你砍下了他们的头 长官\N{\fs14\}You severed their heads, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:02.89,1:23:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,除了被我放走的那个\N{\fs14\}Except for the one I spared
Dialogue: 0,1:23:05.25,1:23:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我让他回去替我送个口信\N{\fs14\}so he could return and deliver a message.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:08.36,1:23:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他们想要卸下我的指挥权\N{\fs14\}If they wanted to relieve me of my command,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:11.17,1:23:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,就得来这里找我 然后亲自动手\N{\fs14\}they’d have to meet me here, and do it themselves.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:15.77,1:23:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这里曾经是个军械库\N{\fs14\}This used to be a weapons depot.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.63,1:23:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,在猿流感刚开始时 他们把这里改造成了一个军营\N{\fs14\}They turned it into a relocation camp when the crisis was just beginning.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:23.90,1:23:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不过武器还在这里 就在山里面\N{\fs14\}But the weapons are all still here, inside the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:28.29,1:23:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,会有多少人到这里来\N{\fs14\}How many men will be coming?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:31.79,1:23:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,或许会倾巢而出\N{\fs14\}Probably all of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:33.50,1:23:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不过别想动坏脑筋\N{\fs14\}But don’t get any ideas,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:35.56,1:23:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,除了我 能让他们更害怕的 就只有你们猿类了\N{\fs14\}the only thing they fear more than me is you apes.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:45.55,1:23:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一场圣战\N{\fs14\}This is a holy war.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:51.09,1:23:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,所有人类历史都指向这一刻\N{\fs14\}All of human history has led to this moment.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:55.59,1:24:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们输了 我们将成为最后的人类\N{\fs14\}If we lose, we’II be the last of our kind.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.85,1:24:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的地球会成为你们的猩球 而我们也会成为你们的牲口\N{\fs14\}It will be a planet of apes, and we’II become your cattle.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:08.61,1:24:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,看看你\N{\fs14\}Look at you.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.32,1:24:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得我疯了 对吧\N{\fs14\}You think I am sick, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:22.22,1:24:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我其实并不想杀你儿子\N{\fs14\}I didn’t mean to kill your son.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:26.81,1:24:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果他注定会继承你邪恶的王国\N{\fs14\}But if his destiny was to inherit your unholy kingdom...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.47,1:24:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我很高兴我了结了他\N{\fs14\}I am glad I did.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:36.67,1:24:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,退后\N{\fs14\}Get back!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:47.17,1:24:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我就说你太感情用事了\N{\fs14\}So emotional!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:56.50,1:24:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你内心非常纠结\N{\fs14\}I see how conflicted you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:59.70,1:25:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你已经搞不清自己的目标了\N{\fs14\}You are confused in your purpose.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:03.23,1:25:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你对我的所作所为感到愤怒 但这就是战争\N{\fs14\}You’re angry at me for something I did that was an act of war.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:08.63,1:25:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,但现在你已经注入了太多私人恩怨\N{\fs14\}But you’re taking this all much far too personally.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:14.96,1:25:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,动动你的脑子 如果你杀了我\N{\fs14\}What do you think my men would have done to your apes,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.88,1:25:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我的人会怎么处置你的同类\N{\fs14\}if you had killed me?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:23.15,1:25:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,还是说杀了我对你来说更重要\N{\fs14\}Or is killing me more important?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:37.92,1:25:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,到处都是士兵 我们要怎么进去\N{\fs14\}Soldiers everywhere! How will we get in?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:42.84,1:25:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,得想办法进去 必须得进去\N{\fs14\}Must get in somehow... Must get in!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:48.76,1:25:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,要进去吗\N{\fs14\}In? In?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.08,1:25:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs14\}No!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:52.98,1:25:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不能进去 不\N{\fs14\}No go in! No!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:02.96,1:26:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,朋友 朋友 不能进去\N{\fs14\}Friends! Friends! No! No go in!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:06.63,1:26:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不能进去\N{\fs14\}No go in!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:11.46,1:26:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,朋友 朋友\N{\fs14\}Friend! Friend!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:17.82,1:26:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢 谢谢 朋友\N{\fs14\}Thank you. Thank you, friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.37,1:27:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你救了我们的命\N{\fs14\}You save our lives!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.09,1:27:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\pos(160,25)}逃出地狱之路
Dialogue: 0,1:27:49.66,1:27:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,生了病的人类 肯定就是从这里逃走的\N{\fs14\}Sick humans must have escaped down here!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:59.40,1:28:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不 不 别 别爬 别\N{\fs14\}No, no! No, no climb! No!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:18.53,1:28:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,什么 你看到了什么\N{\fs14\}What? What you see?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:28.12,1:28:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在哪里\N{\fs14\}Wonder where we are.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:29.97,1:28:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\pos(192,25)}猴灾泛滥
Dialogue: 0,1:28:54.70,1:28:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 不 朋友\N{\fs14\}No! Friend...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:01.06,1:29:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs14\}No!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:05.41,1:29:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不\N{\fs14\}No! No!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:07.61,1:29:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不 回来 回来\N{\fs14\}No! Come, come!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:13.78,1:29:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,回来 回来 回来\N{\fs14\}Come! Come, come.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.01,1:29:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不 回来\N{\fs14\}No! Come!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:18.99,1:29:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,回来 回来 快回来\N{\fs14\}Come! Come, come!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.08,1:29:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,科巴\N{\fs14\}Koba...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:00.09,1:30:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,睡吧\N{\fs14\}Sleep.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:02.32,1:30:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你救不了他们的\N{\fs14\}You cannot save them.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:06.62,1:30:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,猿类都将死在这里\N{\fs14\}Apes all die here.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:13.23,1:30:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不会的  - 会的\N{\fs14\}- No! - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:17.75,1:30:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我走吧\N{\fs14\}Join me...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:37.28,1:30:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,如果明早他还活着的话\N{\fs14\}If he's still alive in the morning...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:44.63,1:30:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,就让他回去和其他猿类一起干活\N{\fs14\}He goes back to work as everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:48.32,1:30:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不然就杀了他\N{\fs14\}Or you shoot him.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:50.87,1:30:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,快来 快来 快来\N{\fs14\}Come. Come. Come.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:57.51,1:31:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,她到里面去了\N{\fs14\}She go in!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:06.79,1:32:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,渴吗\N{\fs14\}Thirsty?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:25.88,1:34:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,躲起来 快\N{\fs14\}Hide. Quick.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:38.58,1:34:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,人类会杀了她的\N{\fs14\}Humans will kill her!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:42.21,1:34:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道该怎么做 你们快走\N{\fs14\}I know what to do! Go!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:17.60,1:36:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你还有其他同伴吗\N{\fs14\}Are there others out there?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:27.22,1:36:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,搜查附近一带\N{\fs14\}Sweep the area.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:29.98,1:36:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,把他关进围栏里\N{\fs14\}Put him in the pen.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:14.33,1:37:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉好点了吗\N{\fs14\}Feeling better?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:23.11,1:37:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那就好 那我们可以计划逃跑的事了\N{\fs14\}Good. Then we can talk about escape.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:29.07,1:37:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,团结才会强大\N{\fs14\}Apes together strong!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:40.46,1:37:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们既是开始  - 也是终结\N{\fs14\}- We are the beginning! - And the end!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:06.86,1:38:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,居然还活着\N{\fs14\}Still alive.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:40.05,1:38:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,让他单独去采石场\N{\fs14\}Send him to the quarry. Alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:45.44,1:38:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,等等\N{\fs14\}Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:05.72,1:39:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么\N{\fs14\}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:11.63,1:39:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会出现在这里\N{\fs14\}How did this get in there?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:16.52,1:39:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,带他去干活\N{\fs14\}Get him to work.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:31.35,1:39:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,37\N{\fs14\}Thirty-seven.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:43.69,1:39:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,55\N{\fs14\}Fifty-five.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:47.18,1:39:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,到大伙儿的笼子需要37步\N{\fs14\}Thirty-seven steps to the adult cage.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:49.55,1:39:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,到孩子们那儿需要55步\N{\fs14\}Fifty-five to the children.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:31.00,1:40:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道 等到墙建好了 上校就会杀了所有猿类\N{\fs14\}You know, Colonel shoot apes when wall is done.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:40.33,1:40:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这墙是疯狂之举\N{\fs14\}This wall is madness.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:44.44,1:40:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,根本救不了他\N{\fs14\}It won't save him.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:47.93,1:40:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,就像它同样也救不了你\N{\fs14\}Anymore than it will save you.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:50.37,1:40:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我自己会救我自己\N{\fs14\}I save myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:53.17,1:40:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你身上还有什么值得被拯救吗\N{\fs14\}Is there anything left of you to save?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:20.54,1:41:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我挖的\N{\fs14\}I do.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:39.13,1:41:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都回到笼子里了吗\N{\fs14\}Apes going back to the cage?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:44.82,1:41:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你 非常勇敢\N{\fs14\}You are very brave.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:49.50,1:41:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- 勇敢？ - 勇敢\N{\fs14\}- Brave? - Brave!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:52.64,1:41:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,勇敢\N{\fs14\}Brave!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:59.26,1:42:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,猿类？\N{\fs14\}Ape?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:02.78,1:42:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我 是猿类吗\N{\fs14\}Me? Ape?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:13.42,1:42:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你是\N{\fs14\}You are...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:27.19,1:42:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,诺娃\N{\fs14\}Nova.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:31.26,1:42:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,诺娃\N{\fs14\}Nova.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:43.93,1:42:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,来 来 快来看看\N{\fs14\}Come! Come! Come to see!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:46.05,1:42:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,过来看\N{\fs14\}Come to see!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:48.11,1:42:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,来 快来看\N{\fs14\}Come! Come to see!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:05.56,1:43:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,34，35，36，37！30！37！\N{\fs14\}34, 35, 36, 37! 30! 37!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:13.22,1:43:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我挖的\N{\fs14\}I do.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:17.09,1:43:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,现在怎么办\N{\fs14\}What now?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:27.29,1:43:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,干吗\N{\fs14\}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:35.03,1:43:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs14\}No!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:39.11,1:43:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不 不 不\N{\fs14\}No, no! No, no!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:47.15,1:43:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs14\}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:54.18,1:44:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我和你们提到的那个同类\N{\fs14\}This is the ape I told you about!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:58.74,1:45:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\fs14\}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:17.85,1:45:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,坏猴子\N{\fs14\}Bad Ape.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:21.50,1:45:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,坏猴子\N{\fs14\}Bad Ape.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:25.01,1:45:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,坏...猴子\N{\fs14\}Bad... Bad Ape.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:39.34,1:45:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,出什么事了\N{\fs14\}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:00.87,1:46:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不能继续挖了 不然整个隧道都会被水淹没的\N{\fs14\}We can't keep digging! It will flood the whole tunnel!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:04.27,1:46:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,可不挖我们就没法到孩子们那里\N{\fs14\}If we don't, we can't reach the children!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:26.75,1:46:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我们必须时刻关注下面的情况\N{\fs14\}We must keep looking down there...
Dialogue: 0,1:46:28.68,1:46:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,另找办法到孩子们那儿去\N{\fs14\}Find another way to reach the children.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:30.92,1:46:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我们必须马上离开 会有更多士兵到这里来\N{\fs14\}We must leave now! More soldiers are coming!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:35.15,1:46:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,人类会相互残杀 也会杀死我们\N{\fs14\}Humans will destroy each other! And us with them!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:43.71,1:46:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,只能从地面把孩子们救出来\N{\fs14\}We’II have to get the children out above ground.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:46.46,1:46:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么救\N{\fs14\}How?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:24.29,1:47:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你们这些畜生\N{\fs14\}You animals!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:46.12,1:47:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是谁干的\N{\fs14\}Who did that?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:54.57,1:47:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,到底是谁\N{\fs14\}Who was it?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:03.67,1:48:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是你\N{\fs14\}Was it you?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:57.96,1:50:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱你 儿子\N{\fs14\}I love you, son.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:09.99,1:51:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,走 快走\N{\fs14\}Go, go.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:28.54,1:51:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,快点 我们走\N{\fs14\}Hurry! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:34.80,1:51:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,凯撒 怎么了\N{\fs14\}Caesar, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:47.69,1:51:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,赶紧 你快走吧\N{\fs14\}Hurry. You must go.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:50.18,1:51:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,留下你一个吗\N{\fs14\}Without you?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:52.65,1:51:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不行\N{\fs14\}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:54.57,1:51:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,毛里斯说得对\N{\fs14\}Maurice was right.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:01.09,1:52:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,现在的我就像科巴\N{\fs14\}I am like Koba.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:06.15,1:52:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,他当年不能放下他的仇恨\N{\fs14\}He could not escape his hate.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:16.47,1:52:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在也无法放下我的\N{\fs14\}And I still cannot escape mine.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:25.10,1:52:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,走 快走 快走\N{\fs14\}Move! Go, go! Go! Go! Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:13.56,1:53:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,上校 上校\N{\fs14\}Colonel! Colonel!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:18.16,1:53:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,他到底人在哪里\N{\fs14\}Where the hell is he?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:06.27,1:58:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,快点\N{\fs14\}Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,1:59:04.07,1:59:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,上校 你在里面吗 上校\N{\fs14\}Colonel, are you in there? Colonel?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:48.77,1:59:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,驴子 去拿榴弹发射器\N{\fs14\}Donkey! Grenade launcher!
Dialogue: 0,2:00:48.64,2:00:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你在搞什么鬼 蠢驴 把发射器给我\N{\fs14\}God damn it, donkey! Get me the launcher!
Dialogue: 0,2:01:40.99,2:01:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\pos(160,25)}开始及结束
Dialogue: 0,2:09:12.33,2:09:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,别担心\N{\fs14\}Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:18.53,2:09:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,毛里斯\N{\fs14\}Maurice...
Dialogue: 0,2:09:23.68,2:09:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你们现在都到家了\N{\fs14\}You are home now.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:31.88,2:09:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,猿类很强大\N{\fs14\}Apes are strong...
Dialogue: 0,2:09:38.45,2:09:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不管有没有我\N{\fs14\}With or without me.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:10.12,2:10:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,儿子会知道\N{\fs14\}Son will know...
Dialogue: 0,2:10:17.71,2:10:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,谁是他的父亲\N{\fs14\}who was father.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:34.97,2:10:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,还有\N{\fs14\}And what...
Dialogue: 0,2:10:39.28,2:10:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,凯撒\N{\fs14\}Caesar did...
Dialogue: 0,2:10:46.50,2:10:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,为我们做的一切\N{\fs14\}for us.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:53.50,2:11:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,凯撒\N{\fs14\}Caesar...
